<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpen sepaih I hiu,
 Thisan a tat I hiu;
 Lal Krista a dinga do di'n,
 Sepaih in I kipieu;
 Lauh um ah I um zing,
 Mahleh lawpa lasa'n;

[V2]
 Lalpen sepaih Lawi-upa chun,
 I lunggil A hih hat.
 Lalpen sepaih I hiu,
 A pahchak la saitiu;
 Muonum in A na sem hitiu,
 I Lalpen lopi chuh.

[V3]
 2. Lalpen sepaih I hiu,
 A min kipak a pu'n;
 Lal Krista kikhetden laia,
 Kross chunga kitak chuh;
 Lalpen sepaih I hiu,
 Manna punna'n ngaiin;
 I Lal Isu min chawihat na'n,
 Haksa cheng thuok ngapin.

[V4]
 3. Lalpen sepaih I hiu,
 Mi deihloh chanpih in;
 Tun Amah I thuokpi u chun,
 A kawmah lang hitiu;
 A puonlap dawmsang un,
 Hun sawt hita puona;
 Lopina ni ahung nai tai,
 Lalpen sepaihte di'n.</lyrics>
<title>SOLDIERS OF THE KING</title>
<hymn_number>314</hymn_number>
</song>